Uses of Package
org.openwms.tms

Packages that use org.openwms.tms
Package
Description
org.openwms.tms
The outer module package contains functional interfaces and entities.
org.openwms.tms.commands
This package contains all types required for asynchronous Command handling.
org.openwms.tms.events
This package contains all types required for asynchronous Event handling.
org.openwms.tms.impl
This package contains the implementation classes that shall not be used directly only through interfaces.
org.openwms.tms.impl.redirection
This package contains classes according to TransportOrder redirection.
org.openwms.tms.impl.removal
This package contains logic for participating in the removal strategies.
org.openwms.tms.impl.state
This package contains logic for TransportOrder state management.

    Class
    Description
    DeniedException
    A DeniedException is thrown by a DecisionVoters in case a business action is not allowed to be executed.
    Message
    A Message is used to encapsulate a message text with an identifier.
    Message.Builder
    Message builder static inner class.
    PriorityLevel
    A PriorityLevel is used to prioritize TransportOrders.
    StateManager
    A StateManager is able to manage the state of a TransportOrder.
    TransportationFacade
    A TransportationFacade is a transactional Spring managed bean that is independent from the used API exporter pattern.
    TransportationService
    A TransportationService offers some useful methods regarding the general handling of TransportOrders.
    TransportOrder
    A TransportOrder is used to move TransportUnits from a current Location to a target.
    TransportOrderState
    A TransportOrderState defines all possible states a TransportOrder may resist in.
    TransportServiceEvent.TYPE
    All possible types of this event.
